###
### HEROKU DEPLOYMENT
###

@heroku_url = https://flower-store-reboot-oop-ad9a74de098a.herokuapp.com

### Get all flowers (HEROKU)
GET {{heroku_url}}/api/v1/flower

### Get all users (HEROKU)
GET {{heroku_url}}/api/v1/users

### Create user on Heroku
POST {{heroku_url}}/api/v1/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "heroku.user@example.com",
  "dob": "1995-05-15"
}

### Create flower on Heroku
POST {{heroku_url}}/api/v1/flower
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "ROSE",
  "color": "BLUE",
  "sepalLength": 3.0,
  "price": 18.99
}

### Create order on Heroku
POST {{heroku_url}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "items": ["ROSE", "TULIP"],
  "payment": "credit-card",
  "delivery": "dhl"
}

### Simulate delivery (HEROKU)
GET {{heroku_url}}/api/v1/delivery/simulate?method=dhl&itemType=ROSE

### Simulate payment (HEROKU)
GET {{heroku_url}}/api/v1/payment/simulate?method=paypal&amount=50.00

